From the Infowars web site :: Alex cuts through government deceit and disinformation on this explosive Tuesday, November 12 edition of The Alex Jones Show. 

Only a day after we broke the news that the feds are now deploying public microphones capable of recording conversations across America, we have now confirmed today that white boxes hoisted about the streets of Seattle can track your every move as you stroll through the city. In response to this intrusive surveillance and other unconstitutional abuses, American lawyer and activist Larry Klayman joins the show to talk about the Reclaim America Now Coalition. 

Robert Mazur, the man who successfully infiltrated the Medellin Cartel in Columbia, also joins the broadcast to reveal how corrupt mega banks stay above the law while laundering money for crime syndicates with complete impunity.
